Lonmin Says Production Hit by Unprotected Strike at Karee in South Africa

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-05-20T07:57:30Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-20/lonmin-says-production-hit-by-unprotected-strike-at-karee-in-south-africa.html
Lonmin Plc (LMI)  said production at its
Karee operations in  South Africa  has been affected by industrial
action by members of the  National Union of Mineworkers  since the
night shift on May 17.  Lonmin commented in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  